        <mxCell id="4" value="&lt;b&gt;Context&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;Only local windows are drawn inside each panel. Commits outside the panel still exist but are omitted for space.&lt;br&gt;Omitted early false positives: C6 = 0.89, C9 = 0.94, C12 = 0.91. Most other omitted commits have risk 0.02." style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;arcSize=8;fillColor=#f5f5f5;strokeColor=#d9d9d9;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;spacingLeft=10;spacingRight=10;fontSize=12;" vertex="1" parent="1">
