        <mxCell id="70" value="&lt;b&gt;Step 3&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;RWLB-S stops with C16(P) and C19(F).&lt;br&gt;Interval handed to bisection: (C16,C19]. The midpoint C17 is the culprit here, so bisection finishes in 1 realized step.&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Total: 2 lookback + 1 realized bisect = 3&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;Worst-case bisection for this 3-commit interval would still be 2." style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;arcSize=6;fillColor=#ffffff;strokeColor=#d9d9d9;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacingLeft=10;spacingTop=8;fontSize=12;" vertex="1" parent="1">
