        <mxCell id="81" value="&lt;b&gt;Step 1&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;Scan left from C23 until risk exceeds T = 0.90.&lt;br&gt;C22 = 0.02 &lt; T&lt;br&gt;C21 = 0.50 &lt; T&lt;br&gt;C20 = 0.93 &gt; T, so C20 is the trigger and the tested commit is the one just before it: C19." style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;arcSize=6;fillColor=#ffffff;strokeColor=#d9d9d9;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacingLeft=10;spacingTop=8;fontSize=12;" vertex="1" parent="1">
